### 3. 레포지토리 인터페이스

**`/user-service/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/FollowRepository.kt`**

```kotlin
package com.maum.backend.repository

import com.maum.backend.domain.follow.Follow

interface FollowRepository {
    fun save(follow: Follow): Follow
    fun delete(followerId: String, followeeId: String)
    fun existsByFollowerIdAndFolloweeId(followerId: String, followeeId: String): Boolean
    fun findAllByFolloweeId(followeeId: String): List<Follow>
